00:00:17.330 --> 00:00:20.830 line:93%
GIRLFRIEND

00:00:20.920 --> 00:00:22.250 line:93%
CALLING

00:00:41.770 --> 00:00:44.110 line:93%
<i>The person you have reached
is unavailable. Please leave...</i>

00:00:50.950 --> 00:00:52.320 line:93%
<i>Please, pick up.</i>

00:00:53.030 --> 00:00:55.200 line:93%
<i>I have this phone for three more days.</i>

00:00:55.950 --> 00:00:57.540 line:93%
<i>I want to hear your voice.</i>

00:00:58.210 --> 00:01:00.170 line:93%
<i>I want to say I'm sorry.</i>

00:01:01.210 --> 00:01:02.290 line:93%
<i>And I miss you.</i>

00:01:19.230 --> 00:01:20.440 line:93%
She won't pick up, right?

00:01:21.440 --> 00:01:24.270 line:93%
Ji-ho is totally normal, huh?

00:01:24.520 --> 00:01:27.110 line:93%
Unlike you, she's good
with facing reality.

00:01:28.530 --> 00:01:29.360 line:93%
Oh, gosh!

00:01:30.030 --> 00:01:31.030 line:93%
What's his problem?

00:01:32.320 --> 00:01:34.030 line:93%
He had a fight with Captain Yoo again.

00:01:34.830 --> 00:01:36.910 line:93%
It looked like Jung-woo
was really going to kill him,

00:01:37.370 --> 00:01:39.040 line:93%
so Lieutenant Paeng brought him here.

00:01:43.380 --> 00:01:47.420 line:93%
He's clearly affection-deprived.
He's always clinging onto people,

00:01:47.590 --> 00:01:50.920 line:93%
but he starts up with them first.
He's clingy to you too, right?

00:01:51.050 --> 00:01:53.470 line:93%
Yeah, you nailed it.
I'm affection-deprived.

00:01:54.640 --> 00:01:56.720 line:93%
You must be Brainy Smurf.

00:02:11.360 --> 00:02:13.070 line:93%
He's smart.

00:02:13.990 --> 00:02:16.410 line:93%
How did you know I was affection-deprived?

00:02:17.280 --> 00:02:19.580 line:93%
My mom cares only about money.

00:02:20.910 --> 00:02:24.120 line:93%
When I was studying in Japan
and came home after two years,

00:02:24.960 --> 00:02:27.170 line:93%
and when my maternal grandma passed away,

00:02:27.500 --> 00:02:30.090 line:93%
my mom opened the restaurant and worked.

00:02:31.630 --> 00:02:33.930 line:93%
She likes money much more

00:02:34.180 --> 00:02:36.220 line:93%
than her one and only son.

00:02:36.970 --> 00:02:38.350 line:93%
I was always lonely.

00:02:40.220 --> 00:02:43.310 line:93%
A lot of kids from rich families
are affection-deprived like you.

00:02:45.600 --> 00:02:46.650 line:93%
Hey.

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:50.690 line:93%
I hear your family owns
Master Yoo's Spicy Shortribs. Right?

00:02:52.490 --> 00:02:55.070 line:93%
Wow. I went there yesterday,
and they opened another wing.

00:02:56.360 --> 00:02:58.620 line:93%
You went there yesterday? With whom?

00:03:06.120 --> 00:03:07.170 line:93%
No comment.

00:03:08.500 --> 00:03:09.590 line:93%
You're dating, aren't you?

00:03:10.920 --> 00:03:15.090 line:93%
Gosh. The poor woman.
She's dating a player.

00:03:15.880 --> 00:03:19.470 line:93%
I really pity her.
Will you make brownies again?

00:03:20.060 --> 00:03:20.890 line:93%
You punk!

00:03:21.890 --> 00:03:24.270 line:93%
You have lice! Lice!

00:03:24.520 --> 00:03:26.100 line:93%
What? I have what?

00:03:26.190 --> 00:03:27.980 line:93%
Look. Here.

00:03:28.650 --> 00:03:29.900 line:93%
This...

00:03:29.980 --> 00:03:33.110 line:93%
This is lice. Gross. Shit.

00:03:33.690 --> 00:03:34.530 line:93%
Lice...

00:03:35.400 --> 00:03:36.240 line:93%
You bastard.

00:03:37.070 --> 00:03:38.410 line:93%
-It's okay, they'll die.
-Kaist...

00:03:39.200 --> 00:03:40.240 line:93%
YESTERDAY

00:03:40.330 --> 00:03:42.580 line:93%
Why are you giving me so much
when I eat for free?

00:03:43.290 --> 00:03:46.290 line:93%
You're our only eat-free-for-life
customer, so I should give you a lot.

00:03:47.670 --> 00:03:49.380 line:93%
You brought your girlfriend today.

00:03:52.090 --> 00:03:55.170 line:93%
About six or seven months ago,
your boyfriend

00:03:56.010 --> 00:04:00.350 line:93%
came all by himself, and ate all of this
in just 20 minutes.

00:04:03.060 --> 00:04:05.180 line:93%
He was skinny, so I didn't think...

00:04:05.270 --> 00:04:07.810 line:93%
Honey. Don't bother the customers
with your babble.

00:04:07.890 --> 00:04:10.060 line:93%
Go clear that table.

00:04:14.610 --> 00:04:16.700 line:93%
I'm sorry. I was a bit loud.

00:04:16.860 --> 00:04:18.360 line:93%
-Not at all.
-Enjoy.

00:04:18.450 --> 00:04:19.990 line:93%
Let us know if you need more.

00:04:21.200 --> 00:04:22.240 line:93%
Enjoy.

00:04:27.790 --> 00:04:29.170 line:93%
The owner is super scary.

00:04:30.290 --> 00:04:32.670 line:93%
Come to think of it, their son's got guts.

00:04:33.340 --> 00:04:36.090 line:93%
How did he do drugs
when his mom is so scary?

00:04:38.680 --> 00:04:40.970 line:93%
Their son did drugs?

00:04:41.050 --> 00:04:43.970 line:93%
Yeah. He's in our prison.
In the same cell as Je-hyeok.

00:04:46.730 --> 00:04:47.560 line:93%
Is he nice?

00:04:47.640 --> 00:04:50.810 line:93%
No one in prison is nice
except for your brother.

00:04:53.520 --> 00:04:54.570 line:93%
He's kind of...

00:04:55.940 --> 00:04:58.610 line:93%
strange. I can't quite read him.

00:04:59.530 --> 00:05:01.530 line:93%
Your mom is super scary.

00:05:02.570 --> 00:05:05.330 line:93%
How did you do drugs behind her back?

00:05:06.240 --> 00:05:08.330 line:93%
My mom isn't interested in me.

00:05:09.210 --> 00:05:11.250 line:93%
She wouldn't know if I went missing.

00:05:11.330 --> 00:05:13.960 line:93%
-Why you... You brat.
-Seriously... How could you say that?

00:05:15.210 --> 00:05:16.250 line:93%
It's true.

00:05:16.340 --> 00:05:19.050 line:93%
This is why I hate kids
from rich families.

00:05:19.510 --> 00:05:21.550 line:93%
They don't know gratitude.

00:05:22.890 --> 00:05:25.810 line:93%
Joon-ho, remember the rich kid we knew
when we were little?

00:05:26.600 --> 00:05:28.060 line:93%
His dad had a big business.

00:05:28.140 --> 00:05:31.730 line:93%
He had the first Game Boy in our class.

00:05:33.310 --> 00:05:36.270 line:93%
That was the first time
I envied someone for being rich.

00:05:36.780 --> 00:05:38.690 line:93%
Yeah, that's right.

00:05:39.240 --> 00:05:41.490 line:93%
I begged my mom for over a year

00:05:41.570 --> 00:05:43.450 line:93%
and finally got it for my birthday.

00:05:43.700 --> 00:05:46.870 line:93%
I begged for like two to three years
and finally got one.

00:05:48.540 --> 00:05:51.920 line:93%
Do you know how civilians like us live?

00:05:52.500 --> 00:05:54.460 line:93%
I never had a game console.

00:05:57.630 --> 00:05:59.130 line:93%
You don't know anything.

00:06:09.140 --> 00:06:12.350 line:93%
<i>I think my family was
one of the poorest families in Gangbuk.</i>

00:06:13.100 --> 00:06:15.190 line:93%
<i>All I remember from my childhood</i>

00:06:15.610 --> 00:06:18.320 line:93%
<i>-is the frequent moving...</i>
-I'm going to the restaurant.

00:06:18.940 --> 00:06:21.400 line:93%
Mommy, I'm hungry.

00:06:22.200 --> 00:06:24.610 line:93%
I made instant noodles. Eat that.

00:06:25.660 --> 00:06:28.490 line:93%
<i>And instant noodles that my mom
made me every morning</i>

00:06:29.040 --> 00:06:30.450 line:93%
<i>before leaving for work.</i>

00:06:32.290 --> 00:06:33.710 line:93%
Run!

00:06:33.790 --> 00:06:35.210 line:93%
Run!

00:06:49.850 --> 00:06:53.100 line:93%
You stink. Gross.

00:06:53.270 --> 00:06:56.440 line:93%
<i>My clothes were dirty
and I couldn't bathe often,</i>

00:06:56.560 --> 00:06:58.770 line:93%
<i>so I was always left out
since grade school.</i>

00:06:59.230 --> 00:07:02.190 line:93%
<i>No. I shunned everyone else.</i>

00:07:02.740 --> 00:07:04.650 line:93%
<i>I hated jerks like that.</i>

00:07:05.070 --> 00:07:07.570 line:93%
<i>I shunned them because they were annoying.</i>

00:07:08.070 --> 00:07:09.830 line:93%
UI JUNIOR HIGH SCHOOL

00:07:10.410 --> 00:07:14.710 line:93%
<i>My mom saved up like crazy
and opened a restaurant.</i>

00:07:15.120 --> 00:07:18.340 line:93%
<i>From ninth grade, we were well-off enough
that every season,</i>

00:07:18.420 --> 00:07:22.300 line:93%
<i>they bought me name brand shoes,
although they were cheap.</i>

00:07:22.880 --> 00:07:26.180 line:93%
<i>But I was still an outcast.</i>

00:07:26.550 --> 00:07:30.350 line:93%
<i>Of course, I shunned them.
I didn't need friends.</i>

00:07:31.180 --> 00:07:33.520 line:93%
<i>I didn't want to play soccer at all,</i>

00:07:33.890 --> 00:07:36.350 line:93%
<i>and I didn't want to go to Internet cafes</i>

00:07:37.350 --> 00:07:38.860 line:93%
<i>with friends.</i>

00:07:39.520 --> 00:07:40.770 line:93%
<i>I liked being alone.</i>

00:07:44.440 --> 00:07:46.910 line:93%
We need one more player.
Do you want to play?

00:07:50.330 --> 00:07:51.450 line:93%
Play with me.

00:07:55.080 --> 00:07:57.040 line:93%
<i>Ji-won was our class president.</i>

00:07:57.120 --> 00:07:58.380 line:93%
Pass!

00:07:58.460 --> 00:08:00.210 line:93%
<i>Everyone liked him.</i>

00:08:00.290 --> 00:08:02.000 line:93%
<i>He had a great personality.</i>

00:08:02.090 --> 00:08:03.130 line:93%
Shoot! Shoot!

00:08:05.170 --> 00:08:08.550 line:93%
<i>I became his sidekick from that day on.</i>

00:08:09.510 --> 00:08:11.140 line:93%
<i>I liked him from the start.</i>

00:08:11.220 --> 00:08:13.770 line:93%
-Hey! Take it!
<i>-From the start.</i>

00:08:13.850 --> 00:08:14.770 line:93%
Pass! Pass!

00:08:14.850 --> 00:08:16.350 line:93%
<i>I liked everything about him.</i>

00:08:19.100 --> 00:08:22.440 line:93%
JEONGSEON'S SNACKS

00:08:22.520 --> 00:08:24.780 line:93%
Are you brothers? You look identical.

00:08:25.360 --> 00:08:26.400 line:93%
No way!

00:08:27.570 --> 00:08:29.070 line:93%
We're not brothers.

00:08:29.320 --> 00:08:31.950 line:93%
Okay, fine. It's no big deal.

00:08:32.580 --> 00:08:33.540 line:93%
Okay.

00:08:34.410 --> 00:08:35.660 line:93%
We're friends.

00:08:36.910 --> 00:08:38.120 line:93%
Best friends.

00:08:38.870 --> 00:08:39.870 line:93%
Really?

00:08:40.830 --> 00:08:41.960 line:93%
He's my best friend.

00:08:42.630 --> 00:08:43.460 line:93%
Right?

00:08:47.260 --> 00:08:50.180 line:93%
<i>Then, we went to high school.</i>

00:08:50.300 --> 00:08:52.510 line:93%
<i>I transferred to Gangnam,</i>

00:08:53.180 --> 00:08:57.270 line:93%
and Ji-won moved to the US
because of his dad's job.

00:08:58.980 --> 00:09:01.900 line:93%
But still, just once...

00:09:04.230 --> 00:09:07.610 line:93%
Just once, I wanted to say it.

00:09:09.530 --> 00:09:11.320 line:93%
<i>So, I wrote an email.</i>

00:09:12.370 --> 00:09:13.620 line:93%
<i>A love letter.</i>

00:09:20.370 --> 00:09:23.330 line:93%
I finally have the courage to tell you.
I like you. Not as a friend.

00:09:23.420 --> 00:09:24.960 line:93%
I like you as more than a friend.

00:09:25.040 --> 00:09:26.050 line:93%
SEND

00:09:26.630 --> 00:09:28.970 line:93%
<i>I mustered up courage and sent the email.</i>

00:09:34.930 --> 00:09:36.350 line:93%
RECIPIENT: JI-WON SONG

00:09:36.430 --> 00:09:38.180 line:93%
SUBJECT: HI, JI-WON, IT'S HAN-YANG

00:09:38.270 --> 00:09:40.850 line:93%
STATUS: NOT READ

00:09:42.480 --> 00:09:43.980 line:93%
<i>And then I deleted it right away.</i>

00:09:44.060 --> 00:09:45.610 line:93%
CANCEL

00:09:45.690 --> 00:09:46.780 line:93%
<i>I just...</i>

00:09:47.780 --> 00:09:49.490 line:93%
<i>couldn't send it.</i>

00:09:56.910 --> 00:09:57.830 line:93%
INBOX

00:09:57.910 --> 00:09:59.620 line:93%
Hi, Ji-won. It's Han-yang.

00:09:59.700 --> 00:10:02.870 line:93%
I'll go to the airport to see you off.
I like you. Not as a friend.

00:10:02.960 --> 00:10:04.460 line:93%
I like you as more than a friend.

00:10:05.920 --> 00:10:08.630 line:93%
<i>We only stayed in touch after that.</i>

00:10:09.380 --> 00:10:11.670 line:93%
He returned to Korea,

00:10:12.050 --> 00:10:15.890 line:93%
and we met again junior year in college
at our junior high school reunion.

00:10:16.510 --> 00:10:19.640 line:93%
Then, Ji-won asked me out first.

00:10:20.810 --> 00:10:22.350 line:93%
Ji-won asked me.

00:10:23.940 --> 00:10:25.940 line:93%
That's when we started dating.

00:10:28.860 --> 00:10:30.650 line:93%
Why did I start talking about that?

00:10:36.830 --> 00:10:37.910 line:93%
I guess...

00:10:38.830 --> 00:10:40.910 line:93%
So, you went to a co-ed school?

00:10:41.960 --> 00:10:43.920 line:93%
Plenty of girls are good at soccer.

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:45.290 line:93%
Ji-won

00:10:46.500 --> 00:10:47.630 line:93%
is a guy.

00:10:54.760 --> 00:10:56.890 line:93%
It feels so good to say it out loud.

00:10:58.100 --> 00:10:59.890 line:93%
I feel free.

00:11:02.390 --> 00:11:03.890 line:93%
We're even now.

00:11:06.980 --> 00:11:10.530 line:93%
I pretended not to know
that you two were best friends,

00:11:11.530 --> 00:11:13.070 line:93%
so do the same for me.

00:11:15.820 --> 00:11:16.990 line:93%
Please.

00:11:23.580 --> 00:11:26.830 line:93%
I knew you two were close friends,
but wow,

00:11:26.920 --> 00:11:29.540 line:93%
you were friends since grade school.

00:11:29.630 --> 00:11:32.760 line:93%
No wonder you two seemed so close.

00:11:36.470 --> 00:11:38.220 line:93%
I didn't tell you, did I?

00:11:39.390 --> 00:11:40.640 line:93%
We're childhood friends.

00:11:43.020 --> 00:11:44.480 line:93%
You knew too.

00:11:45.520 --> 00:11:46.890 line:93%
Thanks for playing dumb.

00:11:49.610 --> 00:11:51.650 line:93%
Just eat your ice cream.

00:11:52.110 --> 00:11:54.530 line:93%
It's okay. I know you're shocked.

00:11:55.070 --> 00:11:57.110 line:93%
You're terrible actors.

00:12:12.670 --> 00:12:15.880 line:93%
PRISON PLAYBOOK

00:12:16.720 --> 00:12:18.130 line:93%
AUTHORIZED PERSONNEL ONLY

00:12:20.140 --> 00:12:23.850 line:93%
Wow. Je-hyeok Kim is amazing.
Simply amazing.

00:12:24.890 --> 00:12:26.810 line:93%
I thought he was kidding.

00:12:27.020 --> 00:12:30.610 line:93%
I never thought he'd ask to put him
back in their cell.

00:12:30.690 --> 00:12:32.520 line:93%
He's an athlete.

00:12:32.980 --> 00:12:34.980 line:93%
He looks dumb, but he knows how to win.

00:12:35.570 --> 00:12:37.490 line:93%
It's a good idea. It is.

00:12:38.070 --> 00:12:40.990 line:93%
Whatever. It's easier said than done.

00:12:41.870 --> 00:12:45.580 line:93%
A storm is about to hit that cell.
It's imminent.

00:12:47.540 --> 00:12:49.500 line:93%
<i>Delivery!</i>

00:13:20.490 --> 00:13:22.780 line:93%
Have a nice day.

00:13:33.920 --> 00:13:35.800 line:93%
Stop it. Not you too.

00:13:39.010 --> 00:13:41.130 line:93%
-We should distribute the items.
-Yeah.

00:13:43.010 --> 00:13:45.560 line:93%
I think the people in our cell
are too nice.

00:13:45.640 --> 00:13:48.680 line:93%
How could we take in that scumbag?
We should just...

00:13:49.180 --> 00:13:50.140 line:93%
Okay.

00:13:50.730 --> 00:13:53.440 line:93%
Everyone gather round.
I ordered apricot tea.

00:13:53.520 --> 00:13:55.440 line:93%
It's hot. Let's drink some cold tea.

00:14:11.080 --> 00:14:13.790 line:93%
Hey. Come here.
We ordered one for you too.

00:14:13.880 --> 00:14:15.130 line:93%
You don't have a summer blanket.

00:14:16.250 --> 00:14:18.630 line:93%
-Jung-woo, you ordered it, right?
-I did.

00:14:22.970 --> 00:14:26.300 line:93%
Hurry up. You're embarrassed, aren't you?

00:14:28.600 --> 00:14:29.770 line:93%
He makes me nervous.

00:14:29.850 --> 00:14:33.350 line:93%
You've been glaring at us
and trying to be scary,

00:14:33.440 --> 00:14:37.820 line:93%
so you feel too awkward and humiliated
to try to get along now, right?

00:14:37.900 --> 00:14:41.900 line:93%
It's okay. He was a total prick
when he first came too.

00:14:43.240 --> 00:14:45.620 line:93%
-Hey you. Come here.
-What?

00:14:46.200 --> 00:14:49.290 line:93%
Stop hiding in the corner there,
and come eat with us.

00:14:56.250 --> 00:14:57.670 line:93%
-Hurry!
-Hurry!

00:14:57.750 --> 00:14:59.000 line:93%
-Do as you're told!
-Hurry!

00:14:59.090 --> 00:14:59.920 line:93%
Listen to the adults.

00:15:00.000 --> 00:15:01.630 line:93%
-You won't listen?
-One, two...

00:15:01.710 --> 00:15:03.260 line:93%
-Seriously.
-Good.

00:15:03.340 --> 00:15:06.140 line:93%
-Punk.
-I'll shave off all your hair.

00:15:06.890 --> 00:15:09.140 line:93%
Okay, today's delivery.

00:15:09.640 --> 00:15:12.270 line:93%
Milk. It'll spoil, so take them. One each.

00:15:12.350 --> 00:15:14.020 line:93%
There are six. Perfect.

00:15:15.230 --> 00:15:17.310 line:93%
-I had a Banana Kick.
-Hey.

00:15:18.940 --> 00:15:20.650 line:93%
-Are you happy?
-Sit comfortably.

00:15:21.610 --> 00:15:23.150 line:93%
-Who ordered socks?
-Me.

00:15:26.660 --> 00:15:28.780 line:93%
Min-chul, let's have the tea later.

00:15:28.950 --> 00:15:30.950 line:93%
This takes a lot of effort.

00:15:31.040 --> 00:15:34.290 line:93%
You said to gather to have apricot tea,
but you won't serve it?

00:15:34.370 --> 00:15:37.040 line:93%
-They'll be okay, right?
-Of course.

00:15:37.880 --> 00:15:39.290 line:93%
Am I the only one who sees

00:15:40.090 --> 00:15:41.500 line:93%
Crony's new boss?

00:15:47.550 --> 00:15:51.100 line:93%
Really? I'll get the ice.

00:15:51.180 --> 00:15:53.640 line:93%
-Then you do it.
-Put that down.

00:15:54.600 --> 00:15:56.440 line:93%
You can't take the last one, you bastard.

00:15:57.230 --> 00:15:58.350 line:93%
What?

00:15:59.190 --> 00:16:01.570 line:93%
Really? Why?

00:16:02.360 --> 00:16:04.190 line:93%
I got the warden's permission.

00:16:04.860 --> 00:16:07.240 line:93%
Crony will return to our cell,

00:16:08.070 --> 00:16:09.660 line:93%
and he will help me train.

00:16:09.740 --> 00:16:12.740 line:93%
No. What if he tries something again?

00:16:14.580 --> 00:16:17.000 line:93%
I'm sure Je-hyeok has a plan.

00:16:17.080 --> 00:16:19.330 line:93%
He has a reputation
for being a troublemaker,

00:16:20.250 --> 00:16:21.670 line:93%
so no prison will take him anyway.

00:16:22.170 --> 00:16:25.380 line:93%
Even if they do, it'll take time,

00:16:25.460 --> 00:16:28.510 line:93%
so I figured it would be better
