Why are you keeping that trash with you?

00:18:42.390 --> 00:18:43.350 line:93%
Huh?

00:18:44.230 --> 00:18:45.060 line:93%
Why?

00:18:48.070 --> 00:18:50.030 line:93%
Have you lost your fricking...

