I played until junior high.

00:22:42.360 --> 00:22:43.730 line:93%
I never played catcher, though.

00:22:44.360 --> 00:22:46.780 line:93%
I can do it.
I'm good at anything physical.

00:22:54.830 --> 00:22:56.040 line:93%
He's a total cyborg.

00:23:00.080 --> 00:23:01.330 line:93%
He's gifted in sports.

00:23:30.700 --> 00:23:31.820 line:93%
That's enough.

