-Stop it, you punk.
-Just a minute.

00:23:59.680 --> 00:24:01.770 line:93%
-Stop it. You're being a stalker.
-What?

00:24:01.850 --> 00:24:03.060 line:93%
This isn't stalking.

00:24:03.770 --> 00:24:05.900 line:93%
Stay still. You've done plenty.

00:24:08.110 --> 00:24:09.530 line:93%
Don't do it. Give me that.

00:24:09.610 --> 00:24:11.610 line:93%
-What's wrong with you?
-Don't do it.

00:24:11.700 --> 00:24:13.110 line:93%
Wait.

00:24:16.030 --> 00:24:18.160 line:93%
What's wrong with you?
Let me make one call.

00:24:18.240 --> 00:24:20.250 line:93%
-What? What's wrong with you?
-Wait.

00:24:20.370 --> 00:24:22.870 line:93%
-Just one call.
-Crony can't see that.

00:24:22.960 --> 00:24:24.080 line:93%
Keep it down.

00:24:24.250 --> 00:24:25.580 line:93%
I said, don't.

00:24:26.250 --> 00:24:28.210 line:93%
-Don't do it.
-Just one minute.

00:24:28.300 --> 00:24:29.590 line:93%
-No.
-Stop.

00:24:30.630 --> 00:24:31.840 line:93%
You bastard.

00:24:39.010 --> 00:24:41.810 line:93%
You don't have to do that.
Just do your thing.

00:24:46.810 --> 00:24:48.690 line:93%
Do what you want to do. It's okay.

00:25:02.410 --> 00:25:05.920 line:93%
If you have nothing to do,
give Min-chul a shoulder massage.

00:25:20.720 --> 00:25:23.430 line:93%
He took orders his entire life.

00:25:23.520 --> 00:25:25.940 line:93%
Telling him to do whatever he wants

00:25:26.190 --> 00:25:27.850 line:93%
is the hardest thing for him.

00:25:28.860 --> 00:25:31.900 line:93%
Look at Han-yang.
He did whatever he wanted all his life.

00:25:32.780 --> 00:25:34.320 line:93%
Look at him. Look at that punk.

00:25:34.400 --> 00:25:37.360 line:93%
He wants another beat down
from Captain Yoo.

00:25:45.710 --> 00:25:47.210 line:93%
How sad. You missed.

00:25:51.040 --> 00:25:54.300 line:93%
I warned you several times
not to touch my things.

00:25:55.090 --> 00:25:56.590 line:93%
I won't take it anymore.

00:25:58.390 --> 00:26:00.600 line:93%
I'm going to kill you, you bastard.

00:26:00.680 --> 00:26:01.760 line:93%
Who wants spicy noodles?

00:26:04.310 --> 00:26:05.980 line:93%
The noodles saved you.

00:26:13.150 --> 00:26:14.780 line:93%
That druggie bastard.

00:26:18.820 --> 00:26:21.200 line:93%
What did you do to the instant noodles?

00:26:21.280 --> 00:26:24.040 line:93%
It tastes absolutely incredible.

00:26:24.120 --> 00:26:27.660 line:93%
It tastes just like the real thing.
It's better than what I had in the army.

00:26:27.750 --> 00:26:28.790 line:93%
How did you do it?

00:26:29.370 --> 00:26:30.330 line:93%
It's easy.

00:26:30.920 --> 00:26:34.750 line:93%
First, soak the noodles in Sprite
for 30 minutes.

00:26:34.840 --> 00:26:37.220 line:93%
<i>Then the noodles become nice and sweet.</i>

00:26:37.300 --> 00:26:40.840 line:93%
But the most important thing is the sauce.

00:26:41.430 --> 00:26:43.970 line:93%
<i>Mix the instant noodles seasoning,
the flakes, apricot tea,</i>

00:26:44.060 --> 00:26:46.270 line:93%
<i>and three spoons of Sprite.</i>

00:26:46.350 --> 00:26:50.560 line:93%
<i>Finally, add one-third tablespoon
of sesame oil for the finishing touch.</i>

00:26:50.650 --> 00:26:55.690 line:93%
This is the Kaist special spicy noodles
passed down for generations in Munrae.

00:26:56.360 --> 00:26:58.450 line:93%
You're really good with your hands.

00:26:59.070 --> 00:27:01.110 line:93%
He made those hooks too.

00:27:04.780 --> 00:27:08.290 line:93%
Tell him if you need anything.

00:27:09.040 --> 00:27:13.040 line:93%
He is a total scumbag,
but he's very talented.

00:27:13.290 --> 00:27:14.590 line:93%
He can make anything.

00:27:17.760 --> 00:27:20.680 line:93%
It's been a while, Han-yang. Right?

00:27:21.340 --> 00:27:25.510 line:93%
How dare you pretend to be Looney
and deceive us. Get over here.

00:27:26.100 --> 00:27:27.470 line:93%
Get over here, you bastard.

00:27:28.520 --> 00:27:31.640 line:93%
I said to get over here. Fine.
I'll go to you. You're dead.

00:27:31.730 --> 00:27:32.900 line:93%
Refrain yourself.

00:27:32.980 --> 00:27:35.480 line:93%
Hey. Je-hyeok. Stay out of it.
You keep taking his side.

00:27:35.570 --> 00:27:37.320 line:93%
That's why he's like that. Let go.

00:27:37.400 --> 00:27:39.240 line:93%
I don't understand what you said.

00:27:40.900 --> 00:27:43.660 line:93%
You get over here too, you bastard.
I guess you envied my tongue.

00:27:43.740 --> 00:27:46.700 line:93%
I'll make yours just like mine.
Min-chul, hold his arm.

00:27:46.780 --> 00:27:47.660 line:93%
Arm...

00:27:47.740 --> 00:27:50.080 line:93%
-Not me. Grab him.
-Chul-doo Kang.

00:27:51.120 --> 00:27:52.620 line:93%
-You have mail.
-Who cares?

00:27:52.710 --> 00:27:54.790 line:93%
I'm going to cut their tongues...

00:27:54.880 --> 00:27:57.500 line:93%
-Let go.
-It's from Cheongju.

00:27:58.090 --> 00:27:58.920 line:93%
Six letters.

00:28:00.300 --> 00:28:01.760 line:93%
Let go. Okay.

00:28:04.550 --> 00:28:05.640 line:93%
What's with him?

00:28:05.720 --> 00:28:07.600 line:93%
It's been a while
since you had a jail date.

00:28:07.680 --> 00:28:09.100 line:93%
-Yeah.
-Good luck.

00:28:09.180 --> 00:28:11.890 line:93%
I know. Thank you so much.

