00:37:58.850 --> 00:38:01.390 line:93%
<i>I'll smash my right hand with a hammer.</i>

00:38:04.060 --> 00:38:06.850 line:93%
<i>Please answer.
I have this phone for three more days.</i>

00:38:06.940 --> 00:38:10.360 line:93%
<i>I want to hear your voice.
