00:38:11.480 --> 00:38:12.570 line:93%
<i>And I miss you.</i>

00:38:12.650 --> 00:38:14.110 line:93%
<i>I miss you, Ji-ho.</i>

00:38:14.190 --> 00:38:16.820 line:93%
<i>I want to hear your voice.
Answer the phone.</i>

00:38:16.900 --> 00:38:19.370 line:93%
<i>I was wrong. I'm a loser, aren't I?</i>

00:38:19.740 --> 00:38:22.080 line:93%
<i>So please, answer the phone. Please.</i>

00:38:36.670 --> 00:38:39.800 line:93%
FALL, 2017

00:38:52.110 --> 00:38:54.530 line:93%
-I guess it's going well for you both.
-Yes.

00:38:54.610 --> 00:38:56.820 line:93%
-How old is she?
-Mine is 33.

00:38:56.900 --> 00:38:58.360 line:93%
Mine is 25.

00:38:59.950 --> 00:39:01.160 line:93%
We're the same age.

00:39:06.290 --> 00:39:08.330 line:93%
That's ridiculous.

00:39:08.410 --> 00:39:10.380 line:93%
You want to die?

00:39:10.460 --> 00:39:11.790 line:93%
You're both the same age.

00:39:11.880 --> 00:39:13.290 line:93%
It's absurd, right?

00:39:13.880 --> 00:39:17.300 line:93%
It's just that I hate to believe
that he and I are the same age.

00:39:17.380 --> 00:39:19.340 line:93%
But I'm not saying we're friends.

00:39:19.430 --> 00:39:23.600 line:93%
I'm saying let's just say it's true
for the sake of argument.

00:39:24.850 --> 00:39:27.600 line:93%
You look like that. With that face...

00:39:27.680 --> 00:39:31.520 line:93%
How could you be only 25?
That's ridiculous.

00:39:31.770 --> 00:39:32.770 line:93%
Show me your ID.

00:39:32.860 --> 00:39:34.860 line:93%
Ask Lieutenant Paeng.

00:39:34.940 --> 00:39:36.780 line:93%
Who cares about age?

00:39:36.980 --> 00:39:41.450 line:93%
My girlfriend is getting out next week.
She says she'll come visit.

00:39:41.910 --> 00:39:45.450 line:93%
She says she'll put her hair up
and wear rose-scent perfume.

00:39:46.450 --> 00:39:47.700 line:93%
Can we have visits now?

00:39:48.040 --> 00:39:50.500 line:93%
We couldn't have visits for a while
because of the new flu.

00:39:53.710 --> 00:39:55.920 line:93%
That's why he's in a bad mood.

00:39:57.590 --> 00:39:58.670 line:93%
It was lifted today.

00:39:59.800 --> 00:40:01.260 line:93%
Visitations are allowed again.

00:40:02.140 --> 00:40:03.720 line:93%
-Really?
-Yes.

00:40:04.260 --> 00:40:06.810 line:93%
But there's such a backlog,
they're going in order.

00:40:32.000 --> 00:40:36.880 line:93%
Well... My girlfriend also says
she's getting out next week.

00:40:36.960 --> 00:40:38.710 line:93%
Really? Congratulations.

00:40:39.300 --> 00:40:40.760 line:93%
She's going to visit.

00:40:40.840 --> 00:40:43.090 line:93%
Of course. You're her boyfriend.

00:40:43.760 --> 00:40:45.890 line:93%
With her hair up
and wearing rose scent perfume.

00:40:53.810 --> 00:40:54.850 line:93%
I'm a snake.

00:40:57.150 --> 00:40:58.520 line:93%
Can I see your letter?

00:41:02.360 --> 00:41:04.360 line:93%
The handwriting is different.

00:41:04.990 --> 00:41:06.070 line:93%
They're different people.

00:41:06.660 --> 00:41:07.950 line:93%
How old is she again?

00:41:08.740 --> 00:41:11.250 line:93%
-She's 33.
-She's 25.

00:41:13.710 --> 00:41:15.670 line:93%
My mom always writes like that.

00:41:17.540 --> 00:41:19.590 line:93%
I'll run right on over.

00:41:20.550 --> 00:41:23.220 line:93%
She also wrote "right on over."

00:41:24.090 --> 00:41:27.720 line:93%
This is something people said
a long time ago.

00:41:28.140 --> 00:41:29.890 line:93%
Just how old is she?

00:41:30.220 --> 00:41:31.720 line:93%
The same person wrote these.

00:41:31.970 --> 00:41:35.560 line:93%
One with her left hand,
the other with her right.

00:41:35.810 --> 00:41:36.770 line:93%
Oh, no.

00:41:39.940 --> 00:41:40.820 line:93%
Give her up.

00:41:40.900 --> 00:41:42.400 line:93%
-That's low.
-Yes.

00:41:42.490 --> 00:41:45.110 line:93%
-You give her up.
-I cannot.

00:41:46.030 --> 00:41:47.490 line:93%
I love Lady Hwang.

00:41:47.870 --> 00:41:51.200 line:93%
-I'm in love already.
-Oh, my. You psycho.

00:41:52.120 --> 00:41:54.000 line:93%
You give her up, you bastard.

00:41:54.710 --> 00:41:55.920 line:93%
I cannot.

00:41:56.000 --> 00:41:58.040 line:93%
This is insane.

00:41:59.500 --> 00:42:02.380 line:93%
Jung-woo Yoo, Han-yang Yoo, visitor.

00:42:04.170 --> 00:42:06.300 line:93%
-Are you two brothers?
-Are you nuts?

00:42:06.630 --> 00:42:07.550 line:93%
No, sir.

00:42:10.470 --> 00:42:12.720 line:93%
Why you... Watch it.

00:42:12.810 --> 00:42:14.770 line:93%
Hey. You have a visitor.

00:42:17.060 --> 00:42:19.270 line:93%
I'm sorry. He's very sick.

00:42:21.900 --> 00:42:22.730 line:93%
Here's a gift.

00:42:23.860 --> 00:42:25.950 line:93%
White tulips mean "forgiveness."

00:42:29.820 --> 00:42:32.080 line:93%
-I'm sorry.
-Excuse me.

00:42:33.540 --> 00:42:35.160 line:93%
Don't I have a visitor?

00:42:35.250 --> 00:42:39.580 line:93%
Sorry. There are many people waiting,
so you'll have to wait.

00:42:41.750 --> 00:42:42.840 line:93%
Yes, sir.

00:42:55.060 --> 00:42:55.890 line:93%
Your girlfriend?

00:42:57.270 --> 00:42:59.270 line:93%
-Yes.
-Gosh.

00:42:59.440 --> 00:43:02.230 line:93%
You should've been good to her
while you had her.

00:43:02.940 --> 00:43:05.400 line:93%
I know. I regret it so much.

00:43:08.150 --> 00:43:09.780 line:93%
She's too good for me.

00:43:10.740 --> 00:43:12.330 line:93%
If I can see her again,

00:43:13.660 --> 00:43:15.080 line:93%
I can do anything.

00:43:16.080 --> 00:43:16.910 line:93%
Even break out?

00:43:19.500 --> 00:43:22.340 line:93%
-My girlfriend won't like that.
-Gosh.

00:43:22.420 --> 00:43:26.920 line:93%
The mighty Je-hyeok Kim
is actually whipped.

00:43:30.260 --> 00:43:34.010 line:93%
Just like you, there was a person

00:43:34.760 --> 00:43:38.680 line:93%
that I thought about 24 hours a day...

00:43:46.940 --> 00:43:47.940 line:93%
And?

00:43:49.490 --> 00:43:50.700 line:93%
There was someone that I liked.

00:43:51.410 --> 00:43:52.240 line:93%
What?

00:43:53.160 --> 00:43:54.490 line:93%
You weren't lying?

00:43:55.870 --> 00:43:57.540 line:93%
What do you take me for?

00:43:58.000 --> 00:44:00.960 line:93%
I was really popular when I was young.

00:44:07.920 --> 00:44:09.920 line:93%
<i>A BETTER TOMORROW</i>

00:44:10.010 --> 00:44:14.550 line:93%
WINTER, 1995

00:44:22.600 --> 00:44:25.980 line:93%
I wanted to give it to you last night,
but you were asleep.

00:44:26.070 --> 00:44:27.860 line:93%
You should've woken me.

00:44:28.400 --> 00:44:29.240 line:93%
What for?

00:44:32.610 --> 00:44:35.490 line:93%
-Do you like it?
-Yeah, I do.

00:44:36.660 --> 00:44:39.620 line:93%
-I found...
-You found it on the street?

00:44:40.660 --> 00:44:44.460 line:93%
Why are there so many things dropped
on the road that you take?

00:44:44.540 --> 00:44:45.580 line:93%
Take me next time.

00:44:48.420 --> 00:44:51.340 line:93%
-Is that right?
-Is what right?

00:44:51.880 --> 00:44:53.090 line:93%
That's right.

00:44:55.260 --> 00:44:57.970 line:93%
I found this on the ground too.

00:45:08.820 --> 00:45:11.280 line:93%
Take it. My... My arm is getting tired.

00:45:13.030 --> 00:45:13.860 line:93%
You do it.

00:45:16.450 --> 00:45:17.950 line:93%
You put it on my finger.

00:45:19.620 --> 00:45:20.660 line:93%
You brat.

00:45:23.710 --> 00:45:24.960 line:93%
Alright. There.

00:45:28.210 --> 00:45:29.170 line:93%
I'm leaving now.

00:45:29.250 --> 00:45:31.420 line:93%
I may be late tonight.

00:45:31.510 --> 00:45:34.430 line:93%
I have a gift for you too.

00:45:41.600 --> 00:45:44.520 line:93%
I bought you a pair of sneakers.

00:45:44.600 --> 00:45:46.020 line:93%
I have plenty.

00:45:46.100 --> 00:45:48.980 line:93%
The sole ripped, so it leaks.

00:45:49.060 --> 00:45:53.150 line:93%
Say, "Thank you," and take them
while I'm being nice.

00:45:53.900 --> 00:45:56.450 line:93%
-Weren't they expensive?
-They're counterfeit.

00:45:57.620 --> 00:45:58.870 line:93%
Then I'll take them.

00:46:01.660 --> 00:46:03.160 line:93%
-Goodness.
-That's right.

00:46:03.250 --> 00:46:04.580 line:93%
I have something to say.

00:46:10.500 --> 00:46:11.340 line:93%
What is it?

00:46:13.170 --> 00:46:15.590 line:93%
No. Later. I'll tell you tonight.

00:46:16.090 --> 00:46:18.970 line:93%
-Have a nice day.
-You're so silly.

00:46:19.050 --> 00:46:21.850 line:93%
Wait. I really have something to say.

00:46:24.480 --> 00:46:27.190 line:93%
What? What is it? The sun is going to set.

00:46:30.820 --> 00:46:31.650 line:93%
I love you.

00:46:32.980 --> 00:46:35.150 line:93%
You brat. That's stupid...

00:46:35.240 --> 00:46:36.490 line:93%
I'm leaving.

00:46:37.360 --> 00:46:38.490 line:93%
Lock up.

00:46:38.570 --> 00:46:41.580 line:93%
-Okay. Bye.
-Bye.

00:46:59.550 --> 00:47:01.260 line:93%
You'll be getting out soon.

00:47:02.300 --> 00:47:04.850 line:93%
The suffering is finally almost over.

00:47:07.060 --> 00:47:08.690 line:93%
Mom didn't come again.

00:47:10.480 --> 00:47:13.320 line:93%
It's Saturday. How could she,
with the restaurant?

00:47:15.570 --> 00:47:17.440 line:93%
Still, I thought she'd come at least once.

00:47:19.360 --> 00:47:22.370 line:93%
We opened another wing,
so it's been even crazier.

00:47:23.160 --> 00:47:24.620 line:93%
Be understanding.

00:47:26.580 --> 00:47:27.620 line:93%
I understand.

00:47:29.160 --> 00:47:31.170 line:93%
Money is more important than her child.

00:47:33.040 --> 00:47:36.210 line:93%
She sent her kid to jail to save money
on bail.

00:47:36.710 --> 00:47:37.590 line:93%
I understand.

00:47:37.670 --> 00:47:39.840 line:93%
It was all for you.

00:47:39.930 --> 00:47:42.010 line:93%
That's why she didn't bail you out.

00:47:43.430 --> 00:47:45.060 line:93%
That's all an excuse, Dad.

00:47:46.140 --> 00:47:47.470 line:93%
It isn't an excuse.

00:47:48.930 --> 00:47:51.810 line:93%
She did it so you could grow up
and get your act together.

00:47:52.100 --> 00:47:54.400 line:93%
She reported you that day for you too.

00:48:04.780 --> 00:48:06.870 line:93%
Mom was the one who reported me?

00:48:14.040 --> 00:48:16.000 line:93%
Did Mom report me?

00:48:25.600 --> 00:48:27.560 line:93%
How could she do that?

00:48:38.480 --> 00:48:41.700 line:93%
How... How could she...

00:48:42.610 --> 00:48:43.780 line:93%
How?

00:48:47.790 --> 00:48:48.990 line:93%
She's my mom.

00:48:51.330 --> 00:48:52.160 line:93%
How?

00:48:59.760 --> 00:49:03.550 line:93%
I just submitted the petition
for your retrial.

00:49:12.310 --> 00:49:13.560 line:93%
You've suffered a lot.

00:49:14.560 --> 00:49:16.270 line:93%
You've suffered a lot, my little brother.

00:49:17.560 --> 00:49:19.730 line:93%
No, you've suffered more because of me.

00:49:22.240 --> 00:49:24.200 line:93%
-Thank you.
-Don't say that.

00:49:24.490 --> 00:49:25.780 line:93%
That's ridiculous.

00:49:27.870 --> 00:49:31.370 line:93%
I'm sorry I couldn't do it sooner.

00:49:31.450 --> 00:49:32.580 line:93%
Don't say that.

00:49:33.460 --> 00:49:34.580 line:93%
If it weren't for you...

00:49:36.540 --> 00:49:38.460 line:93%
I may not have been alive today.

00:49:38.540 --> 00:49:40.710 line:93%
Don't say stupid things like that.
Want to die?

00:49:43.670 --> 00:49:44.510 line:93%
Sorry.

00:49:46.930 --> 00:49:48.970 line:93%
All we did was submit the petition.

00:49:50.560 --> 00:49:53.640 line:93%
It may take months
before we get a response.

00:49:54.350 --> 00:49:56.650 line:93%
-I know.
-Don't let it wear you down.

00:49:57.440 --> 00:49:59.190 line:93%
Let's hang in there as we have been.

00:50:05.320 --> 00:50:06.950 line:93%
You should return to work.

00:50:08.030 --> 00:50:09.780 line:93%
It's been a while, right?

00:50:11.790 --> 00:50:14.080 line:93%
We don't know how much longer
this fight will last.

00:50:15.410 --> 00:50:16.670 line:93%
I'm fine now.

00:50:17.330 --> 00:50:21.050 line:93%
I can hang in there,
so return to your university.

00:50:22.380 --> 00:50:24.840 line:93%
Leave the work to the lawyer.

00:50:26.970 --> 00:50:28.800 line:93%
Okay. I'll take care of it.

00:50:28.890 --> 00:50:30.140 line:93%
You may get fired.

00:50:30.260 --> 00:50:31.760 line:93%
I will not.

00:50:32.390 --> 00:50:35.640 line:93%
Why would I get fired?
I'm a popular professor.

00:50:35.730 --> 00:50:37.560 line:93%
So, go back to your job.

00:50:37.640 --> 00:50:39.650 line:93%
-Okay.
-You mean it?

00:50:41.270 --> 00:50:43.320 line:93%
You'll return to work, right?

00:50:43.400 --> 00:50:45.940 line:93%
Then, go back right away.

