01:13:02.050 --> 01:13:05.260 line:93%
It's okay. By the way, it's getting
kind of chilly at night now.

01:13:07.010 --> 01:13:07.970 line:93%
All right, then.

01:13:11.520 --> 01:13:14.770 line:93%
Still, time passes.

01:13:15.900 --> 01:13:17.360 line:93%
It's fall already.

01:13:18.440 --> 01:13:19.400 line:93%
Gosh.

01:13:20.150 --> 01:13:22.320 line:93%
You must be upset you can't have visitors.

01:13:24.240 --> 01:13:25.740 line:93%
This happens now and then.

01:13:27.870 --> 01:13:29.450 line:93%
You're not crying, are you?

01:13:30.040 --> 01:13:31.410 line:93%
I'm about to cry.

01:13:35.290 --> 01:13:39.380 line:93%
Jung-woo, you never went this long
without seeing your brother before, right?

01:13:43.880 --> 01:13:47.890 line:93%
You know, I've never seen brothers

01:13:47.970 --> 01:13:50.510 line:93%
as close as you guys before.

01:13:51.350 --> 01:13:56.230 line:93%
I know. Most brothers are apathetic
and don't talk much...

01:13:56.310 --> 01:13:58.900 line:93%
to each other, aren't they?

01:13:58.980 --> 01:14:00.480 line:93%
We were like that too.

01:14:01.400 --> 01:14:03.940 line:93%
-What?
-That's how we were.

01:14:06.030 --> 01:14:09.870 line:93%
Both my brother and I
aren't very affectionate.

01:14:10.490 --> 01:14:13.700 line:93%
We're 12 years apart,
so we were never close.

01:14:15.000 --> 01:14:17.830 line:93%
We probably spoke
fewer than ten times a year.

01:14:20.170 --> 01:14:23.260 line:93%
OCTOBER 2010

01:14:23.380 --> 01:14:25.300 line:93%
Wow. Seaweed soup?

01:14:29.390 --> 01:14:30.390 line:93%
Is it Mom's birthday?

01:14:32.520 --> 01:14:33.520 line:93%
No, it's my birthday.

01:14:35.100 --> 01:14:35.940 line:93%
Really?

01:14:37.940 --> 01:14:38.980 line:93%
Happy birthday.

01:14:45.650 --> 01:14:48.200 line:93%
Jung-woo is 26 already.

01:14:49.740 --> 01:14:50.950 line:93%
Time really flies.

01:14:54.330 --> 01:14:55.160 line:93%
I'm 23.

01:14:59.250 --> 01:15:00.380 line:93%
He's 23.

01:15:04.960 --> 01:15:08.760 line:93%
SPRING, 2011

01:15:09.510 --> 01:15:12.470 line:93%
Jung-woo, take care of yourself.

01:15:13.220 --> 01:15:14.270 line:93%
Don't get sick.

01:15:26.860 --> 01:15:30.280 line:93%
Train well and call us often.

01:15:30.530 --> 01:15:33.870 line:93%
My baby. It's still so cold out.

01:15:33.950 --> 01:15:35.950 line:93%
It's okay, Dad. It's only four weeks.

01:15:36.500 --> 01:15:37.500 line:93%
Don't worry.

01:15:49.130 --> 01:15:49.970 line:93%
Why did you come?

01:15:51.590 --> 01:15:54.470 line:93%
I had time to kill.

01:15:56.060 --> 01:15:57.060 line:93%
Okay.

01:16:17.370 --> 01:16:18.450 line:93%
Take care.

01:16:19.370 --> 01:16:20.250 line:93%
Okay.

01:16:26.710 --> 01:16:28.760 line:93%
<i>He was really stiff.</i>

01:16:30.470 --> 01:16:32.470 line:93%
<i>As soon as my incident happened,</i>

01:16:32.970 --> 01:16:34.970 line:93%
<i>my brother took a leave of absence
from his school.</i>

01:16:36.470 --> 01:16:38.520 line:93%
And from then until now,

01:16:39.520 --> 01:16:41.270 line:93%
he only worked on my case.

01:16:42.850 --> 01:16:44.400 line:93%
He has no personal life.

01:16:45.190 --> 01:16:47.360 line:93%
He spent 24 hours a day on me.

01:16:48.150 --> 01:16:50.360 line:93%
Wow. How nice of him.

01:16:51.700 --> 01:16:54.700 line:93%
I never even imagined he'd do that for me.

01:16:56.160 --> 01:16:57.030 line:93%
After what happened,

01:16:58.200 --> 01:17:00.080 line:93%
I hated the world.

01:17:02.540 --> 01:17:04.420 line:93%
I wanted to kill everyone,

01:17:05.080 --> 01:17:06.590 line:93%
and I wanted to die.

01:17:07.340 --> 01:17:09.050 line:93%
I felt so wronged and was so angry,

01:17:10.010 --> 01:17:11.380 line:93%
it drove me crazy.

01:17:13.300 --> 01:17:15.550 line:93%
-I was out of my mind.
-True.

01:17:16.550 --> 01:17:18.060 line:93%
You really were.

01:17:20.600 --> 01:17:21.430 line:93%
Aren't you sleeping?

01:17:22.350 --> 01:17:23.270 line:93%
I am.

01:17:26.110 --> 01:17:27.020 line:93%
But...

01:17:28.400 --> 01:17:30.280 line:93%
But once I came to,

01:17:30.860 --> 01:17:32.820 line:93%
we were petitioning for a retrial.

01:17:33.320 --> 01:17:37.320 line:93%
I was just being angry
and annoyed in here,

01:17:38.450 --> 01:17:41.540 line:93%
but I had come this far
thanks to my brother.

01:17:43.710 --> 01:17:48.380 line:93%
Before then, I never thought
I'd actually say things like...

01:17:51.090 --> 01:17:52.300 line:93%
"Thank you,"

01:17:53.510 --> 01:17:54.930 line:93%
or "I love you."

01:17:56.470 --> 01:17:58.600 line:93%
But they come out naturally now
whenever I see him.

01:17:59.930 --> 01:18:01.270 line:93%
It's automatic.

01:18:02.270 --> 01:18:03.770 line:93%
After I came here,

01:18:04.390 --> 01:18:06.100 line:93%
I wrote my sister a letter

01:18:07.440 --> 01:18:09.860 line:93%
for the first time in my life.

01:18:09.940 --> 01:18:12.070 line:93%
At lease little sisters are cute.

01:18:12.150 --> 01:18:16.030 line:93%
My sister's temper is just like mine.

01:18:17.410 --> 01:18:20.870 line:93%
We weren't close,
just like you and your brother were.

01:18:21.910 --> 01:18:23.700 line:93%
But after what happened,

01:18:25.500 --> 01:18:29.080 line:93%
I said a lot of cringy comments
to my sister.

01:18:30.250 --> 01:18:32.670 line:93%
But seriously,

01:18:33.260 --> 01:18:34.800 line:93%
it just comes out automatically.

01:18:35.930 --> 01:18:37.180 line:93%
You guys are lucky.

01:18:38.550 --> 01:18:42.140 line:93%
I'm an only child,
so I have no brothers or sisters.

01:18:43.810 --> 01:18:46.940 line:93%
My mom wanted to save on bail money

01:18:47.560 --> 01:18:49.610 line:93%
and sent her son to jail.

01:18:50.610 --> 01:18:52.360 line:93%
I envy you all.

01:18:53.940 --> 01:18:56.150 line:93%
Didn't your lover report you?

01:18:59.950 --> 01:19:01.700 line:93%
My mom reported me.

01:19:04.500 --> 01:19:07.000 line:93%
My mom is an incredible person.

01:19:08.120 --> 01:19:10.750 line:93%
She's as cold as ice.

01:19:13.250 --> 01:19:14.800 line:93%
She's very strong.

01:19:22.300 --> 01:19:28.310 line:93%
MASTER YOO'S SPICY SHORTRIBS

01:19:39.030 --> 01:19:40.530 line:93%
I'm a crazy witch.

01:19:41.620 --> 01:19:43.120 line:93%
I'm an evil witch.

01:19:43.740 --> 01:19:46.830 line:93%
I was too obsessed with money
to raise my child right.

01:19:49.160 --> 01:19:50.290 line:93%
I...

01:19:51.170 --> 01:19:52.750 line:93%
I deserve to be punished.

01:19:54.710 --> 01:19:55.880 line:93%
My baby.

01:19:56.880 --> 01:19:59.840 line:93%
My poor baby. It must be so hard.

01:20:02.050 --> 01:20:04.260 line:93%
How could my baby be in jail?

01:20:05.930 --> 01:20:08.100 line:93%
My poor baby.

01:20:08.890 --> 01:20:10.060 line:93%
The poor thing.

01:20:32.750 --> 01:20:34.330 line:93%
You know...

01:20:37.710 --> 01:20:38.630 line:93%
Can I...

01:20:39.470 --> 01:20:41.880 line:93%
see Geon-u just once?

01:20:44.680 --> 01:20:46.430 line:93%
Let me see him just once.

01:20:49.810 --> 01:20:53.600 line:93%
Actually, I already asked him.

01:20:53.690 --> 01:20:56.230 line:93%
You did? When is he coming?

01:21:01.900 --> 01:21:03.610 line:93%
He said he didn't want to see you.

01:21:05.620 --> 01:21:07.620 line:93%
He knew it was you.

01:21:08.410 --> 01:21:10.410 line:93%
He said he knew.

01:21:11.040 --> 01:21:14.040 line:93%
Yes. That's why he should come see me.

01:21:14.830 --> 01:21:16.960 line:93%
He said he would never.
Over his dead body.

01:21:19.840 --> 01:21:21.510 line:93%
He said he hates...

01:21:23.510 --> 01:21:24.890 line:93%
having an ex-con father.

01:21:27.850 --> 01:21:29.680 line:93%
He'd be fine with a dad...

01:21:32.100 --> 01:21:34.770 line:93%
who collects trash on the street, but...

01:21:36.190 --> 01:21:37.820 line:93%
not a dad in jail.

01:21:40.320 --> 01:21:41.900 line:93%
He says it makes him sick.

01:21:45.450 --> 01:21:47.700 line:93%
I even gave him my liver.

01:21:50.370 --> 01:21:53.540 line:93%
I even gave him my liver.
Why does he hate me?

01:21:54.710 --> 01:21:56.290 line:93%
That punk...

01:21:57.420 --> 01:21:58.630 line:93%
He shouldn't be like that.

01:21:59.340 --> 01:22:00.380 line:93%
Exactly.

01:22:03.470 --> 01:22:05.470 line:93%
You idiot.

01:22:07.510 --> 01:22:09.640 line:93%
You should've done better.

01:22:10.560 --> 01:22:11.680 line:93%
You should've...

01:22:12.980 --> 01:22:14.940 line:93%
You should've been a better person.

01:22:15.940 --> 01:22:18.060 line:93%
You're being punished.

01:22:18.980 --> 01:22:20.690 line:93%
You abandoned your child...

01:22:21.900 --> 01:22:24.780 line:93%
You abandoned your wife
and did as you pleased!

01:22:24.860 --> 01:22:27.160 line:93%
You're being punished for it!

01:22:28.570 --> 01:22:31.290 line:93%
My gosh! Thank you!

01:22:31.370 --> 01:22:34.200 line:93%
My gosh! Thank you, Lord!

01:22:39.330 --> 01:22:40.170 line:93%
What are you doing?

01:22:40.840 --> 01:22:42.500 line:93%
What are you doing?

01:22:42.590 --> 01:22:45.010 line:93%
I'm just going to see Geon-u's face,
just once.

01:22:45.090 --> 01:22:46.380 line:93%
Where is he? What room number?

01:22:46.470 --> 01:22:48.930 line:93%
He doesn't want to see you.
What's wrong with you?

01:22:49.010 --> 01:22:50.550 line:93%
Yeah, so his dad...

01:22:50.930 --> 01:22:54.680 line:93%
I gave him my liver. Why does he hate me?

01:22:54.770 --> 01:22:57.520 line:93%
Stop lying. You're being ridiculous.

01:22:57.640 --> 01:23:00.440 line:93%
-Geon-u doesn't want to see you!
-Let go.

01:23:00.520 --> 01:23:01.980 line:93%
Let go!

01:23:02.070 --> 01:23:04.690 line:93%
Where's Geon-u? What room number? Tell me.

01:23:05.030 --> 01:23:07.110 line:93%
-Geon-u Kang.
-I'm sorry.

01:23:07.200 --> 01:23:08.410 line:93%
Forget it. Let go.

01:23:08.490 --> 01:23:09.950 line:93%
Let go!

01:23:10.370 --> 01:23:12.410 line:93%
I said to let go!

01:23:12.490 --> 01:23:15.500 line:93%
Let go! I need... Look, I...

01:23:15.950 --> 01:23:18.790 line:93%
I... I need to go...

01:23:18.870 --> 01:23:21.250 line:93%
I need to go see my kid.

01:23:21.920 --> 01:23:23.500 line:93%
Why won't you let me go?

01:23:35.600 --> 01:23:38.940 line:93%
Hey, Geon-u! You bastard.

01:23:44.610 --> 01:23:47.950 line:93%
TEN DAYS LATER

01:23:58.580 --> 01:24:00.250 line:93%
Let's clean up.

01:24:00.330 --> 01:24:02.000 line:93%
Jung-woo, wash the rags.

01:24:03.460 --> 01:24:04.630 line:93%
Is he coming today?

01:24:05.210 --> 01:24:06.840 line:93%
Is Kaist coming?

01:24:06.920 --> 01:24:08.130 line:93%
He's being discharged today.

01:24:24.730 --> 01:24:26.690 line:93%
You may have visitors again
starting tomorrow.

01:24:26.780 --> 01:24:27.940 line:93%
Prepare for your labor.

01:24:29.240 --> 01:24:32.320 line:93%
-Is Lieutenant Paeng away?
-What about Officer Song?

01:24:32.410 --> 01:24:34.410 line:93%
They both went out of town for training.

01:24:34.570 --> 01:24:35.700 line:93%
They'll be back in ten days.

01:24:38.790 --> 01:24:39.830 line:93%
Okay.

01:24:45.250 --> 01:24:47.050 line:93%
Take care of yourself.

01:25:01.480 --> 01:25:03.060 line:93%
They said you have to change into this.

01:25:10.990 --> 01:25:11.990 line:93%
Tell Geon-u...

01:25:15.570 --> 01:25:17.660 line:93%
that his dad loves him a lot.

01:25:21.290 --> 01:25:22.120 line:93%
Okay.

01:25:27.750 --> 01:25:29.880 line:93%
You must be upset you couldn't see him.

01:25:33.300 --> 01:25:34.930 line:93%
No, I'm fine.

01:25:37.600 --> 01:25:39.220 line:93%
I saw him in my dream last night.

01:25:40.100 --> 01:25:41.270 line:93%
He was in your dream?

01:25:42.890 --> 01:25:43.890 line:93%
In my dream...

01:25:45.480 --> 01:25:46.730 line:93%
Geon-u and I...

01:25:52.900 --> 01:25:54.740 line:93%
We ate something yummy at a nice place.

01:25:57.910 --> 01:25:59.330 line:93%
What, did you have steak?

01:26:03.250 --> 01:26:05.290 line:93%
We had super expensive steak

01:26:05.790 --> 01:26:07.750 line:93%
at a super expensive restaurant.

01:26:43.160 --> 01:26:45.540 line:93%
Dad, I'm hungry.

01:26:49.380 --> 01:26:51.840 line:93%
Where's Mom? Isn't she home?

01:26:51.920 --> 01:26:53.380 line:93%
She went to the restaurant.

01:26:53.460 --> 01:26:56.380 line:93%
Find something to eat in the fridge.

01:26:56.470 --> 01:26:58.720 line:93%
I'm sleeping. Don't wake me up.

01:27:05.850 --> 01:27:06.850 line:93%
God...

01:27:11.360 --> 01:27:14.320 line:93%
Let's eat. Eat.

01:27:15.280 --> 01:27:16.700 line:93%
Doesn't it look yummy?

01:27:17.200 --> 01:27:19.780 line:93%
This is Dad's specialty instant noodles.

01:27:19.870 --> 01:27:21.870 line:93%
There are three boiled eggs in there too.

01:27:28.460 --> 01:27:30.330 line:93%
What's wrong with that? Did it break?

01:27:31.000 --> 01:27:32.710 line:93%
It's been a while since it broke.

01:27:33.090 --> 01:27:35.800 line:93%
I asked Mom for a new one,
but she flat-out told me no.

01:28:06.660 --> 01:28:07.870 line:93%
Okay.

01:28:09.080 --> 01:28:10.960 line:93%
-You're awesome.
-Of course.

01:28:11.330 --> 01:28:13.880 line:93%
This is a piece of cake.
This is nothing to me.

01:28:13.960 --> 01:28:16.380 line:93%
We submitted our future
career goals in school today.

01:28:16.670 --> 01:28:18.920 line:93%
-I'm going to change it tomorrow.
-To what?

01:28:19.010 --> 01:28:20.380 line:93%
To someone like you.

01:28:21.510 --> 01:28:23.180 line:93%
Someone like me? What's that?

01:28:23.260 --> 01:28:24.220 line:93%
A scientist.

01:28:25.890 --> 01:28:27.310 line:93%
You're a scientist.

01:28:27.720 --> 01:28:30.890 line:93%
Sure. I'm a famous scientist in Munrae.

01:28:30.980 --> 01:28:32.810 line:93%
If I wanted,

01:28:32.900 --> 01:28:36.980 line:93%
I could make Taekwon V, Gundam,
Grandizer, anything.

01:28:44.320 --> 01:28:46.120 line:93%
-Hello?
-Get over here, punk.

01:28:46.200 --> 01:28:48.950 line:93%
Why aren't you here? A house opened up.

01:28:49.040 --> 01:28:52.460 line:93%
Okay. I'm coming. I'll go now.

01:28:56.380 --> 01:28:57.300 line:93%
I'll be back.

01:29:02.550 --> 01:29:03.390 line:93%
Son.

01:29:05.260 --> 01:29:06.470 line:93%
Later, for dinner,

01:29:08.180 --> 01:29:10.930 line:93%
order yourself some <i>jjajangmyeon</i>, okay?

01:29:32.330 --> 01:29:34.920 line:93%
Are you ready? Let's go.

01:29:39.550 --> 01:29:43.880 line:93%
Officer, can you put the cuffs on me
after we leave the hospital,

01:29:44.430 --> 01:29:46.340 line:93%
in the van?

01:29:46.970 --> 01:29:49.850 line:93%
My son is in the same hospital wing,

01:29:51.140 --> 01:29:53.770 line:93%
and I don't want him to see me.

01:29:59.190 --> 01:30:00.190 line:93%
It's the rule.

01:30:09.330 --> 01:30:10.200 line:93%
Oh, right.

01:30:11.040 --> 01:30:14.160 line:93%
You will be transferred
to Nambu Penitentiary as of today.

01:30:15.670 --> 01:30:17.750 line:93%
It's new, so it has the best facilities.

01:30:17.830 --> 01:30:20.170 line:93%
You're going to the medical wing there.

01:30:27.390 --> 01:30:30.140 line:93%
So, stop cleaning,

01:30:30.220 --> 01:30:32.470 line:93%
and get ready for work.
We don't have time.

01:30:33.390 --> 01:30:35.440 line:93%
How could they transfer him
out of the blue like that?

01:30:37.600 --> 01:30:39.310 line:93%
His things are still here.

01:30:40.230 --> 01:30:42.150 line:93%
-How could they...
-Why you...

01:30:43.030 --> 01:30:45.200 line:93%
What are you talking about?

01:30:46.360 --> 01:30:49.160 line:93%
You people are here
because you committed crimes.

01:30:49.740 --> 01:30:51.030 line:93%
You guys are criminals.

01:30:53.120 --> 01:30:56.410 line:93%
Why must we report things like that
to jerks like you?

01:30:57.790 --> 01:30:59.830 line:93%
The rules prevent us
from telling you, too.

01:31:00.750 --> 01:31:03.840 line:93%
If you want to assert rights like that,
don't commit crimes.

01:31:07.340 --> 01:31:09.010 line:93%
This isn't a club.

01:31:09.680 --> 01:31:11.720 line:93%
Wake the hell up.

01:31:12.890 --> 01:31:14.140 line:93%
This is a prison.

01:31:40.210 --> 01:31:46.260 line:93%
PERSONAL EFFECTS

01:31:55.520 --> 01:31:58.140 line:93%
6 INMATES

01:32:00.150 --> 01:32:02.520 line:93%
5 INMATES

01:32:08.030 --> 01:32:08.950 line:93%
Min-chul.

01:32:10.320 --> 01:32:11.410 line:93%
I have good news.

01:32:13.830 --> 01:32:17.620 line:93%
You were selected
to be released on parole!

01:32:20.210 --> 01:32:22.330 line:93%
Your name will be sent
to the Ministry of Justice soon.

01:32:23.290 --> 01:32:25.090 line:93%
-Do you mean it?
-Of course.

01:32:25.500 --> 01:32:27.630 line:93%
Don't worry. You'll pass, no problem.

01:32:29.130 --> 01:32:31.430 line:93%
You're a model inmate,
have crazy merit points,

01:32:31.510 --> 01:32:34.800 line:93%
and got good officer evaluations.
There's no reason for you not to pass.

01:32:36.390 --> 01:32:39.890 line:93%
Gosh. You really hung in there. Good job.

01:32:43.150 --> 01:32:44.190 line:93%
How many years was that?

01:32:46.190 --> 01:32:47.480 line:93%
It's been over 22 years, right?

01:33:23.270 --> 01:33:25.190 line:93%
<i>He said something harsh.</i>

01:33:25.270 --> 01:33:26.310 line:93%
<i>His feelings were hurt.</i>

01:33:26.400 --> 01:33:28.270 line:93%
<i>What did he say?</i>

01:33:28.940 --> 01:33:32.740 line:93%
<i>Even if everyone else thinks that,
you can't.</i>

01:33:32.820 --> 01:33:36.620 line:93%
<i>They're the worst. They'll go after anyone
if they smell money.</i>

01:33:37.740 --> 01:33:39.160 line:93%
I know that jerk.

01:33:39.240 --> 01:33:41.870 line:93%
<i>-The guards are there.
-You know what this is, right?</i>

01:33:41.960 --> 01:33:44.170 line:93%
<i>Stay still. It's what you like.</i>

01:33:44.250 --> 01:33:46.330 line:93%
<i>-Who likes druggies?
-Three. Two.</i>

01:33:46.420 --> 01:33:47.840 line:93%
<i>-One.</i>
